Package: dbus-mqtt-bridge
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         libsdbus-c++1,
         libyaml-cpp0.8,
         libpaho-mqttpp3-1,
         libpaho-mqtt1.3,
         libncurses6
Description: Bridge between D-Bus and MQTT
 Bridges D-Bus signals and methods to MQTT topics, enabling
 integration between D-Bus services and MQTT-based systems.
 .
 Features:
  - Bidirectional D-Bus to MQTT bridging
  - Configurable mappings via YAML
  - System and session bus support
  - Interactive configuration generator with D-Bus introspection
